:TroubleTicketNote_Network_Interface_Down_006_Note1 noria:troubleTicketNoteCorrelatedExecution :EventRecord_CR01_Interface_Up .

# Final check for connectivity and density:
# - Agents: Linked to resources, application modules, trouble tickets, change requests.
# - Locations: Linked to resources.
# - Product Models: Linked to resources.
# - Resources: Linked to agents, product models, locations, network interfaces, applications, hypervisors, trouble tickets, change requests, event records.
# - Network Interfaces: Linked to resources, network links.
# - Network Links: Linked to network interfaces, resources, trouble tickets.
# - Applications: Linked to resources, application modules, services, trouble tickets, change requests, event records.
# - Application Modules: Linked to applications, services, agents, resources, change requests.
# - Services: Linked to application modules, trouble tickets, change requests.
# - Event Records: Linked to resources, applications, agents, trouble tickets, trouble ticket notes, change requests.
# - Trouble Tickets: Linked to services, applications, resources, agents, event records, trouble ticket notes, operation plans, document attachments.
# - Trouble Ticket Notes: Linked to trouble tickets, agents, event records.
# - Change Requests: Linked to services, applications, resources, agents, operation plans, event records.
# - Operation Plans: Linked to pre/post conditions, change requests, trouble tickets (via characteristic/proposed repair action).
# - Action Pre/Post Conditions: Linked to operation plans.

# The graph is dense and interconnected, covering various aspects of IT operations.
